47 balance from the existing CATS Revenue Reserve Fund. If these reserves
48 must be used by the City to cover any debt service payments due within the
49 current fiscal year, the Authority shall provide an amount sufficient to return
50 the fund balance to the thirty million dollars ($30,000,000) required balance.
